= KNOWN BUGS

* When you enter a new room, the autonod box is automatically checked.
* When you enter a new room, your laptop reverts to its "real" value.
* The cake laptop option does not work, I suspect this is something done by tt.fm.
* If you select a laptop, then click the page icon again, it displays your "real" laptop again.

= FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS

* When I select a new laptop, it doesn't appear immediately, what gives?

    Your laptop can only change when you first become a DJ. In order for the laptop to change, you have to step down from the DJ platform, then step back up.

 